Package messages

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Bitfield
    This class extends Message and provides bitfield as payload for bitfiled type request.
    Choke
    This class extends Message and provides Choke type request for choking nodes.
    Handshake
    This class extends Message and provides Handshake type request during initial connection.
    Have
    This class extends Message and provides Have type request for updating peers of newly received piece.
    Interested
    This class extends Message and provides Interested type request to notify peers they have piece that node wants.
    Message
    Base Class for creating all types of Messages
    MessageWithPayload  
    NotInterested
    This class extends Message and provides Not Interested type request to notify peers they dont have piece that node wants.
    Piece
    This class extends Message and provides piece type request to send content to peers.
    Request
    This class extends Message and provides request type request to request particular piece from peers.
    Unchoke
    This class extends Message and provides UnChoke type request for un-choking nodes.
